            <ul>
                <li><strong>Privacy leaks:</strong> Accidentally sharing your location, full name, or social media profiles can lead to unwanted contact outside the chat.</li>
                <li><strong>Scammers & phishing:</strong> Some users pretend to be friendly to trick you into giving financial details or clicking malicious links.</li>
                <li><strong>Inappropriate content:</strong> On unmoderated platforms, you might encounter explicit material or harassment.</li>
                <li><strong>Catfishing & impersonation:</strong> People may lie about their identity, age, or intentions.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The good news? <strong>You control most of the risk.</strong> By never sharing personal data, using a platform with active moderation, and trusting your instincts, you can drastically reduce the chances of a bad experience.</p>

